Star pattern:-

rows = int(input("enter the no.of rows:"))
for i in range (1, rows+1):
   for j in range (1, i+1):
      print("*", end=" ")
   print ()

Reverse star pattern:-

rows=5
i=rows
while i>=1:
   j=rows
   while j> i:
      print(' ', end=' ')
      j-= 1
   k=1
   while k<=i:
      print ('*',end=' ')
      k+=1
   print ()
   i-=2

Number pattern:-

rows=int(input("enter row value:"))
for i in range (1, rows+1):
   for j in range (1, i+1):
      print (j,end=" ")
   print()
